cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with the application of deep learning, a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV), to automatically extract information from camera trap images. The use of deep learning also falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the potential for real-time data collection, which could fall under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR) or multimedia (cs.MM).
